snippet.title: Innchanted - Releasing March 28 to Steam (Gameplay Trailer)
snippet.description:
Run a Magical Inn with friends! Yarrul’s family Inn has been stolen by an evil wizard landlord! Team up with friends to reclaim your family's legacy. Manage your inn, brew potions, fish, cook, and fight in this hectic & heartfelt magical adventure. Play solo or co-op for 1-4 players.

Innchanted releases March 28, preorder now to save 15%, and receive special exclusive costumes for your characters!

🎮 Preorder now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/13...

💡 Join our Social Media channels for the latest news on Innchanted: 

✅ Twitter: https://twitter.com/Innchanted_Game
✅ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Innchanted/
✅ Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@innchanted
